<td><a href="/wiki/File:Crab_Nebula.jpg" class="image" title="Crab Nebula.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/00/Crab_Nebula.jpg/28px-Crab_Nebula.jpg" width="28" height="28" border="0" /></a></td>
